rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0001
rows.name:
We're getting more and more
refugees from Superbia.

rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0002
rows.name:
Apparently Acedia sank beneath the
clouds, and Superbia and Invidia have
been flooded with refugees from there.

rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0003
rows.name:
That influx has got some Superbians
wanting to jump ship to Gula, since
life seems so much safer around here.

rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0004
rows.name:
If you ask me, the Superbians still have
it pretty good compared to all those
Acedian folk who lost their homes.

rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0005
rows.name:
I could understand if it was people
from Acedia seeking refuge here, but
when most of them are Superbians...

rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0006
rows.name:
If you ask me, they should learn to
cope with a little inconvenience. Feels
like they're taking advantage of us.

rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0007
rows.name:
I mean, I'm not going to turn 'em away.
But I doubt everyone's going to make
them feel very welcome.
